---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="GitOps · 基于ArgoCD的持续交付"
  descripcion="使用ArgoCD实现GitOps驱动的持续交付。Git作为集群状态的唯一事实来源——无需手动kubectl apply，消除配置漂移。"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.3);">
          GitOps
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Git作为全部基础设施的事实来源。
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">
          我们通过基于ArgoCD的GitOps工作流消除手动kubectl apply和配置漂移——部署可追溯、可回滚、通过PR进行审计。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CAPABILITIES -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">ArgoCD配置</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">ArgoCD安装并配置自动同步、剪枝和自愈。5次自动重试应对因瞬时依赖失败的部署。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Git仓库结构</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">Git仓库分离应用清单和平台配置。Kustomize基础配置加环境覆盖层，实现无重复的复用。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Helm Chart即代码</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">所有应用使用Helm chart——版本化、可测试、可复用。环境特定的values文件定义dev与生产的差异，无需重复模板。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">流水线集成</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">构建成功后GitHub Actions更新GitOps仓库——ArgoCD检测到变更并自动同步。生产环境无人直接操作集群。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">漂移检测</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">ArgoCD检测Git中期望状态与集群实际状态之间的任何差异。自愈功能自动回滚未经授权的手动变更。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">审计与回滚</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">完整的部署历史记录存储于Git。通过PR回滚——无需紧急脚本或直接集群访问。谁做了什么、何时操作，始终可追溯。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540;" class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">彻底消除配置漂移。</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-8" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">我们从审计现有部署流程开始，交付基于ArgoCD的完整GitOps工作流。</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
        联系我们
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
